Europe Real Estate










 









 Overview


Carlyle's European real estate team advises investments in commercial property that can be repositioned by updating the existing physical structure as well as improving occupancy rates and rental yields.





Carlyle Europe Real Estate Partners







Launched in 2001 at €427 million, this fund targets opportunistic real estate investments in Europe.













Carlyle Europe Real Estate Partners II







Launched in 2004 at €763 million, this fund targets opportunistic real estate investments in Europe.













Carlyle Europe Real Estate Partners III







Launched in 2007 at €2.2 billion, this fund targets opportunistic real estate investments in Europe.









